# ==================== 嵌套 git 项目(各自有 .git,不能纳入)====================
# 改用 vendor/* 而不是 vendor/ — git 父目录排除后子 negate 无效,
# vendor/* 只排除 vendor/ 第一层但 vendor/ 自身可索引,允许子级 negate
vendor/*
md2wechat-skill/
wechat-article-publisher-skill/

# 例外:fengyun-publish skill 镜像必须跟踪(W1.1 决策, 2026-05-27)
# 原因: ~/.claude/skills/fengyun-publish/ 是 user-level skill, git 不跟踪
# 镜像到 vendor/skills/fengyun-publish/ 才能让 rollback 安全
!vendor/skills/
!vendor/skills/fengyun-publish/
!vendor/skills/fengyun-publish/**

# ==================== 输出:仅保留文档/草稿,中间态全忽略 ====================
